[["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/div[2]/div[2]/p[1]/text()[1]","Tony Tucker, left, remains in a critical condition after a crash that killed his husband Michael James Burnby, 44, right, on October 3."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/div[2]/div[2]/text()[2]","\n    "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/div[2]/text()[4]","\n    "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/div[2]/div[3]/text()[1]"," "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/div[2]/text()[5]","\n"],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/text()[3]","\n\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n"],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/text()[4]","\n                    "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/script[1]/text()[1]","\n                        adsenseDivId = 'adsense_honeytrap'; // used by google_ad_request_done()\n                        adsenseCssStylingClasses = 'honey-trap '; // used by google_ad_request_done()\n                        \n                        google_ad_client = 'ca-fairfax-stuff_js';\n                        google_ad_channel = 'news honeytrap_top_unit';\n                        google_ad_output = 'js';\n                        google_max_num_ads = '1';\n                        google_ad_type = 'text';\n                        google_safe = 'high';\n                        nz.ffx.GoogleAds().displayHoneyTrap();\n                    "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/text()[5]","\n                "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[1]/text()[1]","A critically-injured Christchurch man whose husband was killed by a suspect drunk driver is winning his fight for survival."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[2]/text()[1]","Cruz bar co-owner Tony Tucker is conscious, has smiled and is communicating, but has limited movement and struggles with short-term memory, according to updates on the bar's Facebook page."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[3]/text()[1]","Tucker's husband Michael James Burnby, 44, died in hospital on Wednesday. They were injured when a man, who police suspect had been drinking, drove the wrong way up Salisbury St and struck their Audi on October 3. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[4]/text()[1]","The driver, Aliielua Fesili Salaivao, 38, died at the scene. The crash has led to a petition asking authorities to install warning lights for drivers travelling the wrong way up one-way streets."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[5]/text()[1]","Family members declined to comment on Sunday, but a Christchurch Hospital spokeswoman said Tucker remained in a critical condition."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[6]/text()[1]","On Friday, Cruz bar updated Tucker's condition on "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[6]/a[1]/text()[1]","its Facebook page"],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[6]/text()[2]",", declaring he was conscious, asking questions and mainly breathing unassisted."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[7]/text()[1]","\"He has passed a huge hurdle in his recovery,\" the post said."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[8]/text()[1]","\"6pm Friday: Tony is communicating questions and like the big strong ox he is he seems to have decisively beaten the odds against survival that he was given a few days ago."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[9]/text()[1]","\"Still a few more critical days in ICU [intensive care unit], all going well, and then a very long road ahead, after that. Prayers must be working, because we know he has had thousands of those.\""],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[11]/text()[1]","Cruz bar posted another update on Saturday afternoon when he managed to smile."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[12]/text()[1]","\"It is too soon for him to retain memory of anything for more than a few minutes, but he would be wanting to thank you all so much for all the condolences and for all the love expressed for Mike and for himself."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[13]/text()[1]","\"I'm sure he would be hard out tapping his own message on his tablet with 80 point font and wearing $2-shop glasses if he could move his fingers!\""],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[14]/text()[1]","The deadly crash has prompted "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[14]/a[1]/text()[1]","a petition on Change.org"],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[14]/text()[2]"," calling on the Christchurch City Council to fit flashing lights to the back of one-way intersection traffic lights to warn drivers travelling the wrong way."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[15]/text()[1]","The petition, created by the couple's friend John Lawrence, has more than 500 supporters."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[16]/text()[1]","\"To many people have had near misses or been killed because of people doing this [sic],\" Lawrence wrote."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[17]/text()[1]","\"No one else should ever have to go through what they have had to deal with. Unfortunately one of the most amazing people in the world was killed because of this.\""],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[18]/a[1]/text()[1]","Police said Salaivao"],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[18]/text()[1]"," drove his van through a red light before speeding the wrong way up Salisbury St. He was not wearing a seatbelt and was thrown from the vehicle in the collision just before 11pm on Saturday."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[19]/text()[1]","\n                "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[6]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/article[1]/p[19]/strong[1]/text()[1]","\n                     - Stuff"]]